      "rationale": "Blood viscosity and power-law rheology parameters sourced from the 2025 Q4 calibration dataset (dataVintage 2025-10-15T00:00:00Z). The model was revised on 2026-02-01T00:00:00Z to incorporate updated impeller geometry tolerances and a refined hemolysis transport sub-model. No re-measurement or re-calibration of rheological inputs has been performed against the revised geometry. Re-validation of model inputs is described as planned for Q3 2026 but no completed evidence is available. Input uncertainty bounds carry forward from the pre-revision dataset without adjustment. Achieved level 2.",
